"foo3";"<h2 id=""when-do-we-not-baz"">When do we <em>not</em> baz?</h2>
";"<p>Well, that’s a very good question.</p>
";"<p>Many philosophers have debated it. How about some <span class=""math inline"">\(\text{math}\)</span> instead? Or maybe even some
physics:</p>
<p><span class=""math display"">\[
E=mc^2
\]</span></p>
";"<p>*to the side* Did I get them? Are they distracted? <em>Whew</em>,
thank the gods. I really wouldn’t have liked to tell them the answer.
It’s quite disturbing, that one.</p>
"
